---
title: Hoisin Beef Burgers with Slaw & Golden Fries
description: Upgrade your burgers with these sweet and savoury hoisin-glazed numbers – they still satisfy that burger and fries craving, but with a hint of your favourite Chinese flavours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hoisin-beef-burgers-257ca05c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/hoisin-beef-burgers-5c512589c445fa6ea71bc0e3-344e038d.pdf
